WEBVTT

00:02.735 --> 00:04.399
FELIX (into phone):
We'll be right down.

00:04.400 --> 00:05.934
Car's here.

00:05.935 --> 00:08.167
Your London internship awaits.

00:09.270 --> 00:10.739
Felix, I can't do this.

00:10.740 --> 00:12.374
Of course you can.

00:12.375 --> 00:15.210
Just remember, women are
birds, men are blokes,

00:15.211 --> 00:18.579
and a shag is more than
just a kind of carpet.

00:19.681 --> 00:21.215
Don't shag any blokes.

00:22.684 --> 00:27.225
No, I mean I can't be away
from you for three whole months.

00:27.226 --> 00:27.930
How about this?

00:27.931 --> 00:30.128
We can have breakfast
together every single day

00:30.129 --> 00:32.397
via the miracle of video conferencing.

00:32.398 --> 00:33.632
You can't do that.

00:33.633 --> 00:35.233
That'll be, like, 3:00 a.m. for you.

00:35.234 --> 00:36.401
Nonsense!

00:36.402 --> 00:38.569
Or as they say across
the pond, codswallop.

00:40.238 --> 00:42.040
You're so calm about this.

00:42.041 --> 00:44.376
Just a week ago,
you were begging me to stay.

00:44.377 --> 00:45.978
Well, I thought about it,

00:45.979 --> 00:48.113
and I trust you and I
trust our relationship.

00:48.114 --> 00:49.948
And even though we'll be
an ocean apart,

00:49.949 --> 00:52.149
I couldn't feel more secure.

00:55.320 --> 00:57.322
Where is she?!

00:57.323 --> 00:59.257
Why hasn't she called me?

00:59.258 --> 01:00.325
Maybe she met someone!

01:00.326 --> 01:01.093
Yes, that's it.

01:01.094 --> 01:03.028
I knew this would happen!

01:03.029 --> 01:05.096
(video call ringtone)

01:05.098 --> 01:07.199
Oh, hey, sweetie.

01:07.200 --> 01:09.434
There you are.

01:09.435 --> 01:10.502
<i>Hi, sorry I'm late.</i>

01:10.503 --> 01:13.005
I was out until 2:00 in the morning.

01:13.006 --> 01:15.240
Fergus took all of the
interns to the coolest pub.

01:15.241 --> 01:16.508
<i>(laughs)</i>

01:16.509 --> 01:18.243
That Fergus, what a guy.

01:18.244 --> 01:19.544
Handsome, charming,

01:19.545 --> 01:22.379
always blurring the line
between boss and employee.

01:25.751 --> 01:27.419
Fergus has taught me so much.

01:27.420 --> 01:29.921
This experience has been amazing.

01:29.922 --> 01:32.424
<i>I can't believe that
it's over in three days.</i>

01:32.425 --> 01:33.859
<i>Oh, thank God.</i>

01:33.860 --> 01:36.094
<i>Just three more days until
the ceremonial shaving</i>

01:36.095 --> 01:38.597
<i>of my beard of devotion.</i>

01:38.598 --> 01:40.899
There's a ceremony?

01:40.900 --> 01:42.768
So, what's on tap for today?

01:42.769 --> 01:44.469
Oh, I forgot to tell you!

01:44.470 --> 01:46.405
This morning, I got a text from Fergus.

01:46.406 --> 01:47.905
Yay! More him!

01:50.509 --> 01:53.045
And he is so happy with
what I've been doing

01:53.046 --> 01:54.746
<i>that he asked me to
spend the weekend...</i>

01:54.747 --> 01:56.981
<i>(voice breaking up)</i>

01:58.116 --> 01:59.418
Spend the weekend doing what?

01:59.419 --> 02:00.819
Emily, you froze up.

02:00.820 --> 02:02.287
Doing what?

02:02.288 --> 02:03.721
Hello? Hello?!

02:05.157 --> 02:07.259
Hello?

02:07.260 --> 02:08.493
Damn it!

02:08.494 --> 02:09.894
Which way is England?

02:11.963 --> 02:13.564
Emily, hello?

02:14.633 --> 02:17.069
What is going on?

02:17.070 --> 02:19.336
Oh, just a nightmare.

02:20.439 --> 02:24.242
That moved in with me
and refuses to leave.

02:24.243 --> 02:25.911
I'm looking for a hotspot!

02:25.912 --> 02:27.344
You're about an hour late.

02:29.815 --> 02:31.616
Put your hand down.

02:31.617 --> 02:34.086
EMILY: <i>Felix? Hello?</i>

02:34.087 --> 02:36.588
Oh, good, you're back.

02:36.589 --> 02:38.757
Hi...

02:38.758 --> 02:40.525
guys.

02:40.526 --> 02:42.828
That's a pretty scarf.

02:42.829 --> 02:44.329
Thanks.

02:44.330 --> 02:46.965
There's a woman in Camden
Market who makes them by hand.

02:46.966 --> 02:50.836
Yeah, because now is definitely
the time for scarf talk.

02:50.837 --> 02:52.660
<i>You were saying something
about you and Fergus</i>

02:52.661 --> 02:53.638
<i>and a weekend?</i>

02:53.639 --> 02:54.639
Oh, yes.

02:54.640 --> 02:56.374
He asked me to spend the weekend

02:56.375 --> 02:58.443
designing pieces for the fall line

02:58.444 --> 02:59.811
while he's out of town!

02:59.812 --> 03:01.045
Oh, thank God.

03:02.047 --> 03:03.482
That, um...

03:03.483 --> 03:05.383
that he is recognizing your talent

03:05.384 --> 03:08.820
which was bestowed on you
by our Lord, amen.

03:08.821 --> 03:11.289
All right, well, Felix,
I should go, but...

03:11.290 --> 03:12.657
I love you.

03:12.658 --> 03:13.725
I love you more.

03:13.726 --> 03:15.827
No way, mister... I love <i>you</i> more.

03:15.828 --> 03:17.809
That's impossible, because
I love you so much...

03:18.764 --> 03:22.234
Sorry, I didn't see that ever ending.

03:22.235 --> 03:23.502
I know.

03:23.503 --> 03:25.670
These last three months
have taken quite a toll.

03:25.671 --> 03:27.239
I just miss Emily so much,

03:27.240 --> 03:31.309
and I'm terrified of
someone coming between us.

03:31.310 --> 03:32.877
We know the feeling.

03:35.213 --> 03:37.648
Not the threesome I was hoping for.

03:39.484 --> 03:40.885
Me neither.

